## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the articles reviewed primarily focus on personal development contexts, which may not fully address organizational or systemic change scenarios. Further research could explore empirical studies and broader applications of mindset change in various fields.

